WEBVTT

00:10:29.425 --> 00:10:32.892
and doing things
so that we can polish our résumé

00:10:32.916 --> 00:10:34.586
instead of sitting down

00:10:34.610 --> 00:10:39.129
and reflecting on what we want to do
and who we want to be.

00:10:41.132 --> 00:10:42.398
And so,

00:10:43.624 --> 00:10:47.259
the markers of empathy
in our college graduates

00:10:47.283 --> 00:10:50.426
have been dropping dramatically
in the past two decades,

00:10:50.450 --> 00:10:53.176
while those of narcissism are on the rise.

00:10:53.200 --> 00:10:55.871
There is also a growing culture
of disengagement

00:10:55.895 --> 00:10:58.828
between engineering students
and the public.

00:10:59.611 --> 00:11:04.885
We are trained to build bridges
and solve complex problems